      "content": "Subject: Notice of Consistent Tardiness\n\nDear [Employee's Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I am writing to address a matter that has come to my attention regarding your punctuality during the past two weeks. It has been observed that you have been arriving approximately 15 minutes late to your shifts consistently. While I understand that unforeseen circumstances can arise, it is crucial for the smooth operation of our team that we adhere to the agreed-upon start times.\n\nAs a reminder, punctuality is an essential aspect of our professional environment, and your consistent tardiness has been noted. I kindly request that you make an effort to arrive on time for your shifts moving forward. This will not only demonstrate your commitment to your role but also help maintain the harmony and efficiency of our team.\n\nThank you for your attention to this matter. I am confident that you will address this issue promptly and continue to contribute positively to our workplace.\n\nBest regards,\n\n[Your Name]",
